<p>I am adding Toast Notifications to my desktop application and experiencing strange behavior of Action Center in Windows 10</p>  <p><strong>Observed Behavior:</strong></p>  <ul> <li>Toast Notifications does not appear in Action Center after time out</li> <li>Toast Notifications appear in action center when you click on the action center button during the toast display,but it disappears as<br> soon as you close the action center</li> </ul>  <p><strong>Expected Behavior:</strong></p>  <ul> <li>Toast notifications should appear in Action Center after time out</li> <li>Toast notification should still be there after closing and opening of action center</li> </ul>  <p>Can some one please tell me if this is the defined behavior of Toast Notifications in windows 10 as Microsoft Outlook Toast Notifications behave the same way too. </p>